/*
 * Section
 * -------
 *
 *   Grammar:
 *     - '='+ Title '='+ Space* EolOrEof
 *
 *   The title can contain:
 *     - ExternalLink
 *     - InternalLink
 *     - PageSwitch
 *     - ParserEntity
 *     - PlainExternalLink
 *     - Signature
 *     - Ticks
 *     - XmlElement
 *     - XmlReference
 *
 *   The title cannot contain:
 *     - Newline
 *       - Tables
 *       - Headings
 *       - Horizontal lines
 *       - Block level elements
 *
 *   The title can not contain (syntactically):
 *     - Newlines
 *
 */

